substep.section:
Auth bootstrap goal — the single deterministic owner of authentication infrastructure for the project.
Owns config/packages/security.yaml (firewall, provider, authenticator) and the User entity with password hashing (bcrypt/argon2).
{{#uses_jwt}}Uses lexik/jwt-authentication-bundle as the JWT identity provider; generates the signing keypair.{{/uses_jwt}}
{{^uses_jwt}}Uses the Symfony session/form-login authenticator.{{/uses_jwt}}
See docs/architecture/cross-cutting.md for auth method decisions. See docs/architecture/test-environment.md for test user credentials — never hard-code credentials.

params.param:
[
            "test -f config/packages/security.yaml",
            "vendor/bin/phpstan analyse src/ --level=9",
            "vendor/bin/ecs check src/",
            "vendor/bin/deptrac analyse"
          ]{{#uses_jwt}} plus "bin/console lexik:jwt:check-config"{{/uses_jwt}}
